    <p>GAM­ING MOUSE MAT</p>
    <p>$89.90</p>
    <p>This gam­ing mouse mat is said to be op­ti­mised for track­ing ac­cu­racy and re­spon­sive­ness, thanks to its ul­tra­vi­o­let-light-ac­ti­vated nanobead sur­face, which also has an oleo­pho­bic coat­ing.</p>
    <p>Its rub­berised base has a spe­cial tex­ture that grips the desk, so you can flick and glide your mouse on the mat with con­fi­dence.</p>
    <p>Plus, it is thin at 1.95mm thick and per­fectly flat to min­imise dis­com­fort when your wrist rests or moves along the edge of the mat.</p>

